    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Step inside to an interior that still carries the scent of fresh leather; the upholstery is taut with zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by premium floor mats from day one. Every button, switch, and technological feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service binder documenting every oil change and inspection performed by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning enthusiast. No accidents, no stories, just pure excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
